    {
      "id": "_9eGwykSdQo5UxRkfD2lk",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 556.2477805,
      "y": 146.26171825,
      "width": 926.959716796875,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aJ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1266899587,
      "version": 883,
      "versionNonce": 1620452333,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1775824752389,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "matchsticks 降序 => 核心目的是加速剪枝\n1. 先处理长火柴，放不下了立刻剪枝，避免不必要的搜索\n2. 在逐个放置火柴的过程中，可以让相邻火柴相等的概率更高一些，提高命中率\n在 2 中提到的“命中率”是指：命中不必要的搜索路径，当前边（sides[i]）和前一边（sides[i - 1]）相同\n前一边已经搜过了，当前边不需要再搜了",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "matchsticks 降序 => 核心目的是加速剪枝\n1. 先处理长火柴，放不下了立刻剪枝，避免不必要的搜索\n2. 在逐个放置火柴的过程中，可以让相邻火柴相等的概率更高一些，提高命中率\n在 2 中提到的“命中率”是指：命中不必要的搜索路径，当前边（sides[i]）和前一边（sides[i - 1]）相同\n前一边已经搜过了，当前边不需要再搜了",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "n5Q7ArX4-tMledGFtMK5w",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 556.2477808339845,
      "y": 390.184297,
      "width": 511.45977783203125,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "dlBBlG1oI1aHluiX6BzwI",
        "qXGeUoshAFppJ1Z0Gw96F"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aKG",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 537762701,
      "version": 495,
      "versionNonce": 39181795,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775825866217,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "这里以这个更具代表性的示例来介绍核心流程\n输入：matchsticks = [5, 5, 5, 5, 4, 4, 4, 4, 3, 3, 3, 3]\n输出：true",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "这里以这个更具代表性的示例来介绍核心流程\n输入：matchsticks = [5, 5, 5, 5, 4, 4, 4, 4, 3, 3, 3, 3]\n输出：true",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0z0XXUpi7hafgqTwQLZcX",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 556.247781,
      "y": 321.81640600000003,
      "width": 944.83984375,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aP",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 541078925,
      "version": 263,
      "versionNonce": 1667571277,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1775824752389,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "火柴放置的核心原则 => sides[0 -> n]，能放就放，放不下意味着放错了，逐一回溯，重新探索新的路径。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "火柴放置的核心原则 => sides[0 -> n]，能放就放，放不下意味着放错了，逐一回溯，重新探索新的路径。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "5VKHNFJI9lEpHwARCCBxf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 556.247781,
      "y": 531.36168,
      "width": 960,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
